hawks.html|title=Hawkes Harbor|publisher=SEHinton.com|accessdate=2008-10-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://search.barnesandnoble.com/Hawkes-Harbor/S-E-Hinton/e/9781596001251/?itm=17|title=Hawkes Harbor|publisher=[[Barnes & Noble]]|accessdate=2008-11-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.booksamillion.com/product/B0765305631?id=4255709461190|title=Hawkes Harbor|publisher=[[Books-A-Million]]|accessdate=2008-11-01}}</ref></center> |- | ''Some of Tim's Stories'' | [[Short story|Short stories]] | [[University of Oklahoma Press]] |<center>2007</center> |<center>0</center> |<center><ref name="Tim">{{cite web|url=http://www.sehinton.com/books/tims.html|title=Some of Tim's Stories|publisher=SEHinton.com|accessdate=2008-10-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://search.barnesandnoble.com/Some-of-Tims-Stories/S-E-Hinton/e/9780806138350/?itm=16|title=Some of Tim's Stories|publisher=[[Barnes & Noble]]|accessdate=2008-11-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.booksamillion.com/product/9780142411957?id=4255709461190|title=Some of Tim's Stories|publisher=[[Books-A-Million]]|accessdate=2008-11-01}}</ref></center> |}
